1252
01:24:31,179 --> 01:24:33,086
He's buying the land.

1253
01:24:34,246 --> 01:24:35,314
Our land?

1254
01:24:36,922 --> 01:24:38,058
Get one of the map.

1255
01:24:38,059 --> 01:24:42,092
Make sure to get this and we
wanna get all the pins in there.

1256
01:24:44,582 --> 01:24:45,948
You sure you see this?

1257
01:24:47,399 --> 01:24:49,249
Alright.
How about one at the desk?

1258
01:24:59,877 --> 01:25:01,441
