1262
01:25:14,887 --> 01:25:15,939
Ray...

1263
01:25:17,559 --> 01:25:18,854
I've thought it over.

1264
01:25:20,142 --> 01:25:21,070
Approved.

1265
01:25:24,071 --> 01:25:24,883
Really?

1266
01:25:25,309 --> 01:25:27,177
- Thank you.
