1269
01:25:33,878 --> 01:25:36,547
The hell with that.
I'm gonna roll this out nationally.

1270
01:25:37,513 --> 01:25:41,107
You seen the latest copy of RBM?
Hot off the press.

1271
01:25:44,703 --> 01:25:45,858
Ray, good for you.

1272
01:25:55,745 --> 01:25:57,989
