make a profit, that's fine.

1310
01:28:31,174 --> 01:28:32,893
But don't stop the rest of us.

1311
01:28:32,894 --> 01:28:33,878
Us?

1312
01:28:33,879 --> 01:28:36,746
Us, as in everyone but you.

1313
01:28:36,747 --> 01:28:37,736
Who did you send them to?

1314
01:28:37,737 --> 01:28:38,991
Everyone but you.

1315
01:28:40,405 --> 01:28:43,938
You have no right. You are to
stop this instant, is that clear?

1316
01:28:46,012 --> 01:28:48,722
- Nah.
- What the hell does that mean, nah?

1317
01:28:48,723 --> 01:28:50,998
You will abide by the terms of your deal.

1318
01:28:53,178 --> 01:28:56,716
I am through taking marching orders from you...

1319
01:28:56,717 --> 01:28:59,239
you and your endless parade of NO's.

1320
01:28:59,240 --> 01:29:02,271
Constantly cowering in the face of progress.

1321
01:29:02,272 --> 01:29:05,197
