is your idea of progress...

1322
01:29:05,198 --> 01:29:08,864
you have a profound misunderstand
of what McDonald's is about.

1323
01:29:09,405 --> 01:29:12,870
I have a far greater understanding
of McDonald's than you two yokles.

1324
01:29:12,871 --> 01:29:13,594
What?

1325
01:29:13,595 --> 01:29:15,786
You will do as we say.

1326
01:29:16,161 --> 01:29:17,143
Nope.

1327
01:29:18,737 --> 01:29:20,306
You have a contract!

1328
01:29:27,055 --> 01:29:30,276
You know, contracts are like hearts...

1329
01:29:31,049 --> 01:29:32,411
they're made to be broken.

1330
01:29:47,141 --> 01:29:49,082
Could you please pass the salt?

1331
01:29:52,227 --> 01:29:53,064
Thank you.

1332
01:30:06,436 --> 01:30:08,089
I want a divorce.

1333
01:30:34,401 --> 01:30:36,885
When trying to quietly settle a divorce...

1334
01:30:36,886 --> 01:30:39,407
the first thing to ask is,
what will she want?

1335
01:30:39,408 --> 01:30:42,076
And, is her request reasonable and equitable?

1336
01:30:42,077 --> 01:30:46,893
In terms of marital property there's the house,
and car, savings and checking accounts...

1337
01:30:46,894 --> 01:30:48,093
- Insurance...
- Just give it to her.

1338
01:30:48,094 --> 01:30:49,358
House, car, insurance.

1339
01:30:52,595 --> 01:30:54,093
What about the business?

1340
01:30:57,316 --> 01:30:58,368
Nope.

1341
01:30:59,799 --> 01:31:01,879
Ray, ya have to understand...

1342
01:31:01,880 --> 01:31:03,488
- that she's the...
- K.

1343
01:31:05,700 --> 01:31:07,197
Lemme explain somethin' to ya.

1344
01:31:09,510 --> 01:31:11,681
It's never gonna happen.

1345
01:31:13,980 --> 01:31:19,899
I'd sooner die than give her
