01:32:31,909 --> 01:32:34,403
You put Dick's arches on your letterhead?

1358
01:32:34,404 --> 01:32:35,404
This is not your company, Ray.

1359
01:32:37,901 --> 01:32:40,241
- Do you understand that!?!?
- Mac, don't get upset.

1360
01:32:40,795 --> 01:32:43,910
We came up with the speedy system, not you.

1361
01:32:43,911 --> 01:32:45,533
Us.
What have you ever come up with?

1362
01:32:45,534 --> 01:32:46,703
Can you name one thing?

1363
01:32:46,704 --> 01:32:48,629
You can't, and you never have,
and you never will...

1364
01:32:48,630 --> 01:32:51,657
because you are a leech, Ray.
You are a professional leech.

1365
01:32:50,657 --> 01:32:53,230
You know what I came up with, Mac?

1366
01:32:51,658 --> 01:32:53,230
You know what I came up with, Mac

1367
01:32:53,231 --> 01:32:56,702
A concept.
I came with the concept of winning.

1368
01:32:56,703 --> 01:32:57,790
Lemme talk to him.

1369
01:32:57,791 --> 01:33:00,375
While you two boys were content to sit
back and become a couple of also-rans...

1370
01:33:01,183 --> 01:33:03,025
I wanna take the future.
I wanna win.

1371
01:33:03,026 --> 01:33:06,167
And you don't get there by being
some "aw shucks" guy sap.

1372
01:33:06,168 --> 01:33:08,174
There's no place in business for people like that.

1373
01:33:08,175 --> 01:33:09,590
Business is war.

1374
01:33:09,722 --> 01:33:12,426
It's dog eat dog,
rat eat rat.

1375
01:33:12,427 --> 01:33:17,137
If my competitor were drowning,
I'd walk over and put a hose right in his mouth.

1376
01:33:21,417 --> 01:33:22,578
