1396
01:34:32,025 --> 01:34:32,908
Any stress?

1397
01:34:38,375 --> 01:34:39,136
Okay.

1398
01:34:39,137 --> 01:34:42,037
You need to watch that.
That's a big contributing factor.

1399
01:34:42,967 --> 01:34:46,671
