01:35:43,473 --> 01:35:44,450
Dick.

1413
01:35:44,697 --> 01:35:46,384
There's a card in there.

1414
01:35:49,576 --> 01:35:51,043
Go ahead.

1415
01:35:51,044 --> 01:35:52,185
That's okay.

1416
01:35:52,186 --> 01:35:53,623
No, here. Just...

1417
01:35:54,255 --> 01:35:55,524
You're gonna be happy.

