01:37:27,591 --> 01:37:29,603
Dick McDonald's on the line.

1430
01:37:40,546 --> 01:37:42,208
Hello Dick.

1431
01:37:42,732 --> 01:37:44,559
2.7 million.

1432
01:37:44,690 --> 01:37:47,398
That's a million for each of us after taxes.

1433
01:37:49,857 --> 01:37:54,711
